text: Posts: 54,385 The Latest: Cueto out with none out in 3rd inning of Game 3 (Yahoo Sports) The Royals and Blue Jays are playing Game 3 of the ALCS in Toronto. After an easy first, Cueto allowed 11 of his next 13 batters to reach, while Toronto fans serenaded him with the sing-song chants of ''Cueto-Ceuto'' throughout his outing.
